thread.title: BRIEF-Onemain Holdings Reports Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $1.06

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Onemain Holdings Reports Q4 Adjusted Earnings Per Share $1.06
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Onemain Holdings Inc:
* ONEMAIN HOLDINGS, INC. REPORTS FOURTH QUARTER 2017 RESULTS
* Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $1.06 * Q4 GAAP EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.29 INCLUDING ITEMS * QTRLY NET INTEREST INCOME $653 MILLION VERSUS $567 MILLION
* ORIGINATIONS TOTALED $3.1 BILLION IN Q4 OF 2017, UP 34% FROM $2.3 BILLION IN PRIOR YEAR QUARTER
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $1.05 -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
